meanings: (원래 있던 곳으로) return, come[get, turn] back
(본래의 상태로) return (to), revert to; (의식이) come (a)round, come to
귀가할 때 What time will you come home?
이성교제 Thank you for coming back to me.
실용회화-관계가 안 좋을 때 I want you back.
